> data QueryExpr
>     = Select
>       {qeSelectList :: [(ValueExpr,Maybe String)]
>       ,qeFrom :: Maybe String
>       ,qeWhere :: Maybe ValueExpr
>       ,qeGroupBy :: [ValueExpr]
>       ,qeHaving :: Maybe ValueExpr
>       ,qeOrderBy :: [ValueExpr]
>       } deriving (Eq,Show)

Here is a default value which can be used to easily construct query
expression values.

> makeSelect :: QueryExpr
> makeSelect = Select {qeSelectList = []
>                     ,qeFrom = Nothing
>                     ,qeWhere = Nothing
>                     ,qeGroupBy = []
>                     ,qeHaving = Nothing
>                     ,qeOrderBy = []}

